00:00:56.287 --> 00:01:00.262
=The Demon=

00:01:00.587 --> 00:01:03.250
=Episode 7=

00:01:22.719 --> 00:01:23.480
You're the kindest

00:01:23.480 --> 00:01:24.799
in this world.

00:01:24.879 --> 00:01:26.519
Why don't you show it to everyone,

00:01:26.959 --> 00:01:27.760
Xiao'er?

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:39.079
What... What are you talking about?

00:01:39.079 --> 00:01:40.359
What... What Xiao'er?

00:01:40.359 --> 00:01:41.480
There's nobody here by that name.

00:01:41.599 --> 00:01:43.120
And I don't know anyone by that name.

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:44.599
I don't get it.

00:01:48.879 --> 00:01:49.959
(I'm doomed.)

00:02:04.239 --> 00:02:05.280
Don't worry, Chief Fan.

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:07.159
I'll keep that a secret.

00:02:25.937 --> 00:02:27.275
♪Parasol leaves fall♪

00:02:27.387 --> 00:02:28.637
♪A lonely shadow under the moon♪

00:02:28.637 --> 00:02:30.237
♪A refreshing evening breeze♪

00:02:32.950 --> 00:02:34.375
♪Those whispers♪

00:02:34.437 --> 00:02:35.587
♪Still echo♪

00:02:35.687 --> 00:02:38.100
♪In my heart♪

00:02:39.100 --> 00:02:42.575
♪Dim candle, long windy night♪

00:02:42.787 --> 00:02:45.937
♪Floral fragrance fills the garden♪

00:02:46.987 --> 00:02:52.612
♪Can't shake it from my mind,
it all ends in nothingness♪

00:02:53.237 --> 00:02:55.012
♪Troubling me half my life♪

00:02:55.012 --> 00:02:57.337
♪You're the sleepless wind chime♪

00:02:57.412 --> 00:02:58.712
♪Stirring all my thoughts♪

00:02:58.712 --> 00:03:00.862
♪You're the shooting star
who lights my loneliness♪

00:03:00.925 --> 00:03:02.400
♪Spring comes, autumn goes♪

00:03:02.479 --> 00:03:03.280
Get some good rest.

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:04.160
Wipe your body by yourself.

00:03:04.170 --> 00:03:04.879
What's it?

00:03:07.290 --> 00:03:08.790
It'd be inappropriate
if I helped you with that.

00:03:09.639 --> 00:03:11.240
Are you going to stop massaging me

00:03:11.240 --> 00:03:13.000
because you found out about my identity?

00:03:20.479 --> 00:03:21.400
Fine.

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:23.240
Forget it.

00:03:23.319 --> 00:03:24.199
We're not close

00:03:24.199 --> 00:03:25.560
after all.

00:03:26.439 --> 00:03:27.919
But can you promise

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:30.120
not to tell anyone about

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:31.280
my identity as a cat?

00:03:34.159 --> 00:03:35.719
Sure, rest assured.

00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:39.280
Now you know that,

00:03:39.560 --> 00:03:40.599
as a demon,

00:03:40.759 --> 00:03:42.240
I'm flawed.

00:03:44.759 --> 00:03:45.800
Can you promise me

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:46.759
another thing?

00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:50.879
Don't hurt the other demons

00:03:50.879 --> 00:03:51.960
in the fort.

00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:54.240
Just come at me.

00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:56.199
Sure.

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:57.800
No.

00:03:57.840 --> 00:03:58.719
I mean,

00:03:58.840 --> 00:04:00.199
I will never hurt you.

00:04:00.400 --> 00:04:01.240
Like I said,

00:04:01.520 --> 00:04:02.280
both my father

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:03.360
and I

00:04:03.719 --> 00:04:05.240
never kill the innocent,

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:06.400
be it a human or a demon.

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:07.319
I believe you.

00:04:28.959 --> 00:04:30.360
I will

00:04:30.759 --> 00:04:31.959
keep my word.

00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:34.399
Sure.

00:04:39.439 --> 00:04:40.680
Then starting today,

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:42.079
you need to heed

00:04:42.079 --> 00:04:43.000
my instructions.

00:04:44.279 --> 00:04:45.079
Yes.

00:04:53.480 --> 00:04:54.279
Rong Momo.

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:59.759
Si... Si Ming.

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:02.160
Si Ming is here, Dayao!

00:05:04.439 --> 00:05:05.240
Shush.

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:06.839
I'm not here to cause you trouble.

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:13.560
Do you know me?

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:17.120
Whoever joins the fort

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:19.319
will receive a copy of the name list
of Her Majesty's enemies.

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:21.000
And you top the list.

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:22.279
Of course we all know you.

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:24.600
However,

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:26.279
everyone says you're good-looking.

00:05:30.959 --> 00:05:32.959
To my surprise, you are really handsome.

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:35.720
I'm the number one man in her heart.

00:05:35.720 --> 00:05:36.439
That's right.

00:05:36.720 --> 00:05:37.519
Oh, no.

00:05:37.759 --> 00:05:39.240
It's Mr. Shen now.

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:40.920
Shen Wangchen?

00:05:43.759 --> 00:05:45.120
She puts him first?

00:05:45.279 --> 00:05:46.079
That's right.

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:50.000
What's he like?

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:52.160
Her Majesty said

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:52.879
Mr. Shen

00:05:52.879 --> 00:05:54.519
is our greatest enemy.

00:05:54.920 --> 00:05:57.439
He's talented,

00:05:58.279 --> 00:06:00.040
refined,

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:02.360
and...

00:06:03.519 --> 00:06:04.759
and...

00:06:04.759 --> 00:06:05.959
Pass this to Fan Dayao.

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:07.639
This magical artifact

00:06:07.639 --> 00:06:09.160
can conceal all of her demonic aura.

00:06:10.839 --> 00:06:12.399
Those demon slayers
won't be able to locate her.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:16.439
Why?

00:06:16.759 --> 00:06:18.120
Aren't you a demon slayer?

00:06:19.319 --> 00:06:20.120
I am.

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:22.240
That's why I won't come here again.

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:32.759
Why did Si Ming gift this to me?

00:06:34.040 --> 00:06:34.959
Could it be

00:06:35.600 --> 00:06:37.319
a trap?

00:06:37.959 --> 00:06:38.639
Dayao.

00:06:38.639 --> 00:06:40.639
I've tested it.

00:06:40.639 --> 00:06:42.480
It really conceals one's demonic aura,

00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:44.000
making it a rare valuable.

00:06:44.360 --> 00:06:45.160
This feels off.

00:06:45.959 --> 00:06:47.720
He must be up to something.

00:06:47.720 --> 00:06:48.759
Don't fall for his trap.

00:06:49.439 --> 00:06:50.240
Dayao.

00:06:50.879 --> 00:06:52.040
I think Master Si Ming

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:52.560
gave this to you

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:54.279
for your sake.

00:06:54.319 --> 00:06:56.360
Besides, I think he's into you.

00:06:57.240 --> 00:06:58.160
He's into me?

00:06:58.720 --> 00:06:59.680
That demon slayer?

00:07:06.319 --> 00:07:07.160
You should stay away

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:08.680
from Si Ming after this.

00:07:11.480 --> 00:07:12.360
Why?

00:07:13.439 --> 00:07:14.240
He...

00:07:17.199 --> 00:07:18.079
He's a demon slayer,

00:07:18.079 --> 00:07:18.879
so he's dangerous.

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:20.639
In my opinion,

00:07:20.639 --> 00:07:22.240
he's unlike other demon slayers.

00:07:22.279 --> 00:07:23.839
He seems slow-witted,

00:07:23.839 --> 00:07:25.319
posing no threat to me.

00:07:25.319 --> 00:07:27.120
All right. Focus.

00:07:27.800 --> 00:07:28.519
Starting tomorrow,

00:07:28.519 --> 00:07:29.560
you'll learn how to be a tyrant.

00:07:36.279 --> 00:07:37.079
Dayao.

00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:38.759
Leave me alone.

00:07:57.879 --> 00:07:59.319
Please show your true face.

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:13.600
I don't find this getup

00:08:13.600 --> 00:08:14.959
imposing at all.

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:16.319
Why don't we maintain...

00:08:17.560 --> 00:08:18.680
We'll do as you say.

00:08:32.679 --> 00:08:34.799
What's the point
of practicing how to smile?

00:08:34.919 --> 00:08:36.679
It's a waste of my time!

00:09:10.399 --> 00:09:11.200
Dayao.

00:09:11.679 --> 00:09:13.919
Can you take back this severance pay?

00:09:15.879 --> 00:09:17.000
I don't want to leave.

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:19.200
Mo.

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:21.799
I won't blame you

00:09:21.799 --> 00:09:23.200
for the Truth Serum incident.

00:09:23.200 --> 00:09:24.320
In fact, I'd like to praise you.

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:25.360
If not for you...

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:28.320
If not for you,

00:09:28.399 --> 00:09:31.000
I wouldn't have been able
to recognize my own shortcomings.

00:09:33.320 --> 00:09:35.240
Are you alright, Dayao?

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:41.519
Do your best!

00:09:41.840 --> 00:09:42.840
I have faith in you.

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:45.039
You have a bright future ahead!

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:47.120
Thank you, Dayao!

00:09:47.159 --> 00:09:48.240
I will complete my mission!

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:49.080
Don't mention it.

00:09:52.639 --> 00:09:53.480
Now that's the spirit.

00:09:57.480 --> 00:09:59.519
Young Master, when are you going
to return the demon core?

00:10:00.840 --> 00:10:01.960
Your body...

00:10:01.960 --> 00:10:02.960
I know what to do.

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:06.960
But who's been

00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:08.799
stirring up trouble in this city?

00:10:09.840 --> 00:10:11.360
And what's he after?

00:10:11.559 --> 00:10:12.679
What do you think, Young Master?

00:10:15.919 --> 00:10:17.000
Perhaps all of this

00:10:17.320 --> 00:10:18.840
is the doing of a single man.

00:10:19.720 --> 00:10:21.000
That person harbors sinister intent.

00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:22.960
And there are unspeakable secrets
behind him.

00:10:23.679 --> 00:10:25.159
We must not let our guard down.

00:10:34.240 --> 00:10:35.039
It's true.

00:10:35.519 --> 00:10:36.840
Her Majesty has already learned

00:10:36.840 --> 00:10:38.080
how to be considerate of others.

00:10:38.679 --> 00:10:39.679
I think it's time

00:10:40.279 --> 00:10:41.879
for you to head back.

00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:43.960
Mr. Shen's strategy
has been a brilliant one.

00:10:44.559 --> 00:10:47.120
He actually made Her Majesty
change her ways.

00:10:47.399 --> 00:10:48.200
She now understands

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:50.279
the hardships of us followers.

00:10:50.279 --> 00:10:51.679
I haven't seen Her Majesty in days,

00:10:51.799 --> 00:10:53.919
and I've even started to miss her.

00:10:55.000 --> 00:10:58.720
Then let's go back today.

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:00.000
That won't do.

00:11:00.159 --> 00:11:01.399
Mr. Shen said,

00:11:01.399 --> 00:11:02.559
if Her Majesty is to

00:11:02.559 --> 00:11:04.120
truly learn to make friends,

00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:05.879
we must listen to him.

00:11:06.399 --> 00:11:07.200
Do you

00:11:07.360 --> 00:11:08.559
want Her Majesty

00:11:08.559 --> 00:11:09.519
to have no friends

00:11:09.799 --> 00:11:11.320
and end up a lonely spinster?

00:11:11.917 --> 00:11:13.517
Who says Her Majesty is friendless?

00:11:13.519 --> 00:11:16.240
I think Master Si Ming and Dayao

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:17.759
are getting along very well.

00:11:20.279 --> 00:11:20.879
Well,

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:24.080
I saw Master Si Ming giving Dayao

00:11:24.080 --> 00:11:25.679
a gift.

00:11:26.360 --> 00:11:27.159
Really?

00:11:27.360 --> 00:11:28.799
I knew it, that brat

00:11:28.799 --> 00:11:31.559
has designs on Her Majesty.

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:34.240
No demon slayer would come here often

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:35.919
without taking a single demon.

00:11:37.159 --> 00:11:39.840
A demon slayer and a demon queen.

00:11:40.679 --> 00:11:41.799
What a forbidden love.

00:11:45.159 --> 00:11:46.559
No, no, no.

00:11:47.080 --> 00:11:48.000
I think

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:49.679
Mr. Shen and Her Majesty

00:11:49.679 --> 00:11:50.720
make the best match.

00:11:50.720 --> 00:11:51.759
Think about it.

00:11:51.759 --> 00:11:52.879
If Mr. Shen

00:11:52.879 --> 00:11:54.480
becomes Her Majesty's consort,

00:11:54.519 --> 00:11:57.919
Aowu Fort will surely prosper.

00:11:58.480 --> 00:12:00.559
It's a bright future ahead!

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:11.759
My young master says

00:12:12.039 --> 00:12:13.240
you may head back now.

00:12:17.600 --> 00:12:18.840
One more thing.

00:12:19.480 --> 00:12:20.679
My young master

00:12:20.679 --> 00:12:23.120
is both brilliant and refined.

00:12:23.600 --> 00:12:24.720
He would never fall for

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:25.720
a hot-headed, dull demoness

00:12:25.720 --> 00:12:27.559
like your boss.

00:12:37.879 --> 00:12:41.879
No one is allowed
to speak ill of Her Majesty!

00:12:43.399 --> 00:12:44.039
Darn it!

00:12:44.039 --> 00:12:45.480
Come, let's go find Her Majesty.

00:12:45.480 --> 00:12:46.399
Let's go.

00:12:48.399 --> 00:12:49.200
Momo…

00:12:50.039 --> 00:12:51.039
Momo, they...

00:12:51.080 --> 00:12:52.279
They bullied me

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:54.039
and wouldn't let me tell the truth!

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:56.320
Dayao

00:12:56.559 --> 00:12:58.440
has always been fierce, no?

00:12:59.240 --> 00:13:01.039
No one is allowed to speak ill of Dayao!

00:13:03.480 --> 00:13:05.440
(Si Ming 2-to-1, Shen Wangchen 7-to-1)
Come on, place your bets!

00:13:05.440 --> 00:13:05.799
Here!

00:13:05.799 --> 00:13:06.759
Here, place your bets!

00:13:10.318 --> 00:13:10.998
Come on!

00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:11.759
Do it!

00:13:11.759 --> 00:13:12.639
Here!

00:13:13.159 --> 00:13:14.879
Put in everything you've got!

00:13:14.879 --> 00:13:16.720
(Si Ming 2-to-1, Shen Wangchen 7-to-1)
It's Si Ming! It's him!

00:13:17.679 --> 00:13:19.039
Quick, place your bets!

00:13:19.039 --> 00:13:20.000
I'll bet on Mr. Shen.

00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:21.500
(Si Ming 2-to-1, Shen Wangchen 7-to-1)

00:13:22.679 --> 00:13:23.840
What's that?

00:13:23.840 --> 00:13:25.240
We still can't tell

00:13:25.240 --> 00:13:26.279
who Her Majesty will marry.

00:13:26.279 --> 00:13:27.559
I'll bet on Mr. Shen.

00:13:27.559 --> 00:13:28.559
You all should do the same.

00:13:28.679 --> 00:13:29.720
What's this?

00:13:33.559 --> 00:13:35.039
Just trust me.

00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:39.679
Si Ming and Her Majesty have been having
an undefined relationship for years.

00:13:39.919 --> 00:13:40.879
It's been less than a month

00:13:40.879 --> 00:13:42.360
since Shen's arrival here.

00:13:42.440 --> 00:13:43.919
He's far behind!

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:44.919
I'll bet on Si Ming.

00:13:44.919 --> 00:13:46.279
Yes, Si Ming it is.

00:13:46.600 --> 00:13:48.080
I think Mr. Shen will win.

00:13:48.310 --> 00:13:50.639
You and Siming have been having
an undefined relationship for years?

00:13:51.480 --> 00:13:52.480
What do you mean by that?

00:13:56.519 --> 00:13:57.799
Just wait and see. You'll lose.

00:13:58.000 --> 00:13:58.720
Jiang Li.

00:13:58.720 --> 00:13:59.639
Bet on Mr. Shen!

00:13:59.639 --> 00:14:00.919
Bet on Mr. Shen! Bet on him!

00:14:00.919 --> 00:14:02.879
I trust your taste, sir!

00:14:02.879 --> 00:14:03.604
(Si Ming 2-to-1, Shen Wangchen 7-to-1)

00:14:04.960 --> 00:14:05.759
That's more like it!

00:14:08.759 --> 00:14:11.559
How wonderful. Everyone's back.

00:14:13.399 --> 00:14:15.759
You're truly impressive, Shen Wangchen.

00:14:19.000 --> 00:14:21.399
Mr. Shen! Mr. Shen! Mr. Shen!

00:14:22.039 --> 00:14:23.360
That's more like it!

00:14:24.840 --> 00:14:25.639
Your Majesty.

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:27.279
Have you won Mr. Shen's heart?

00:14:28.360 --> 00:14:30.320
Winning a man over is an easy feat.

00:14:35.799 --> 00:14:37.639
Get over here, Shen Wangchen!

00:15:11.737 --> 00:15:15.400
♪Where did I lose my direction?♪

00:15:15.712 --> 00:15:18.125
♪Only emptiness is left♪

00:15:19.512 --> 00:15:23.287
♪Restless, sleepless, we part ways♪

00:15:23.425 --> 00:15:26.150
♪As sorrow slowly grows within♪

00:15:27.250 --> 00:15:30.737
♪Tears can't heal, smiles still ache♪

00:15:31.112 --> 00:15:34.362
♪Because my heart's with you♪

00:15:34.987 --> 00:15:39.812
♪Your gaze melted the haze♪

00:15:41.262 --> 00:15:48.125
♪Waiting so long for your return♪

00:15:48.987 --> 00:15:56.275
♪The setting sun reminds me of you♪

00:15:56.775 --> 00:16:01.687
♪If the clear sky is torn
by storm and rain one day♪

00:16:02.037 --> 00:16:04.837
♪Tears will flow♪

00:16:05.975 --> 00:16:11.612
♪I will still wait here with no regrets♪

